OL,4,Ctaking Ketamine, family says
OL,6,FDrag queen The Vivienne, who grew up
OL,7,Fin Colwyn Bay, died after taking
OL,8,Fketamine, their family has said.
OL,10,FJames Lee Williams, who won the first
OL,11,Fseries of RuPaul's Drag Race UK under
OL,12,Ftheir drag name, was found dead at the
OL,13,Fage of 32 at their home in Cheshire on
OL,14,FJanuary 5.
OL,16,FTheir manager and friend Simon Jones
OL,17,Fsaid: "James's family and I feel it is
OL,18,Fimportant to say how James tragically
OL,19,Fdied. It was from the effects of
OL,20,Fketamine use causing a cardiac arrest.
