OL,4,Ctaking Ketamine, family says
OL,6,FDonna Chaves, from charity Adferiad -
OL,7,Fwhich operates across Wales and
OL,8,FEngland, said: "We are incredibly
OL,9,Fgrateful to James's family for
OL,10,Fchoosing to support and work with us
OL,11,Fon this campaign. Addiction can affect
OL,12,Fanyone, and too many people suffer in
OL,13,Fsilence due to stigma and lack of
OL,14,Funderstanding.
OL,16,F"By opening conversations and
OL,17,Fchallenging misconceptions, we can
OL,18,Fhelp prevent further tragedies and
OL,19,Fsupport those in need to find hope and
OL,20,Frecovery."
